Ta có
\begin{align*}
y'=12x^2-12x^3,\\
y'=0\Leftrightarrow \left[\begin{aligned}&x=0\\&x=1.\end{aligned}\right.
\end{align*}
Do đó $\min\limits_{[-1;2]}y=\min \{y(-1);y(0);y(1);y(2)\}$, mà $y(-1)=-7$, $y(0)=0$, $y(1)=1$, $y(2)=-16$ nên $\min\limits_{[-1;2]}y=-16$

Ta có $ f'(x)=3x^{2}-6x-9 $. Do đó, $ f'(x)=0\Leftrightarrow\left[\begin{aligned}&x=-1\\ &x=3\end{aligned}\right. $. Khi đó
\begin{align*}
f(-2)=8;&&f(-1)=15;&&f(2)=-12\Rightarrow \max\limits_{[-2;2]}f(x)=15.
\end{align*}
